getContentType

public static IContentType getContentType(PartOfSpeech pos,
                                          IDictionaryDataType type)
Returns the content type (a static final instance) that matches the specified part of speech and file type. If no content type is found for the specified arguments, throws a RuntimeException. Also throws a NullPointerException if the IDictionaryDataType parameter is null

Parameters:
pos - The part of speech of the content type requested; may be null
type - The dictionary file type
Returns:
the content type, if found; null otherwise
